#import <Availability.h>
#ifndef __IPHONE_3_2 #warning "This project uses features only available in iPhone SDK 3.2 and later." #endif

This template provides a starting point for a Couchbase application that uses a split view controller. It provides a user interface configured with a split view controller, two view controllers to manage a master-detail-style display and a Couchbase instance.
